OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778076676
OL,3,CTribute paid to 'wonderful big
OL,4,Cbrother' fatally injured by tree
OL,6,FThe family of a teenager who died
OL,7,Fafter being injured by a fallen tree
OL,8,Fhave said their lives are "shattered
OL,9,Fand will never be the same".
OL,11,FBrodan Dubickas was pronounced dead at
OL,12,FHolmcroft Road in Stafford shortly
OL,13,Fafter emergency services were called
OL,14,Fon Saturday 2 May.
OL,16,FIn a statement released to
OL,17,FStaffordshire Police, the family said:
OL,18,F"On Saturday 2nd May, at 19:33, our
OL,19,Fboy, was tragically and unfairly taken
OL,20,Ffrom us while out playing with his
OL,21,Ffriends in the park.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778076676
OL,3,CTribute paid to 'wonderful big
OL,4,Cbrother' fatally injured by tree
OL,6,F"He truly was the best of us. His
OL,7,Fkindness and generosity were
OL,8,Funmatched, and he lit up a room with
OL,9,Fhis humour and his smile.
OL,11,F"You won't find any bad words said
OL,12,Fabout him, he was loved by so many. He
OL,13,Floved nothing more in life than
OL,14,Fplaying pool, which he managed to get
OL,15,Fto do competitively at least four-
OL,16,Fnights-a-week for the Luck Penny or
OL,17,FStaffordshire Bull "A".
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@TOUyD@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778076676
OL,3,CTribute paid to 'wonderful big
OL,4,Cbrother' fatally injured by tree
OL,6,F"He loved his football, be it playing
OL,7,Ffor Stafford Falcons or refereeing
OL,8,Fmultiple times every weekend. He was
OL,9,Fable to do all this whilst still
OL,10,Fprioritising spending time with family
OL,11,Fand friends.
OL,13,F"A wonderful big brother, he leaves
OL,14,Fbehind three siblings Corey, Kayla and
OL,15,FAmelia whose hearts are breaking right
OL,16,Fnow. He took his role as the eldest,
OL,17,Fwith great pride, and he was always
OL,18,Fthere for them.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778076676
OL,3,CTribute paid to 'wonderful big
OL,4,Cbrother' fatally injured by tree
OL,6,F"As parents, our lives have been
OL,7,Fshattered and will never be the same.
OL,8,FThe pain is unbearable, and the hole
OL,9,Fthat has been left can never be
OL,10,Ffilled. His massive potential will now
OL,11,Fnever be realised, and this is, in
OL,12,Fitself, a tragedy.
OL,14,F"We have been overwhelmed by the
OL,15,Fsupport, generosity and love, sent
OL,16,Ffrom far and wide, to both the family
OL,17,Fand Brodan.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778076676
OL,3,CTribute paid to 'wonderful big
OL,4,Cbrother' fatally injured by tree
OL,6,F"The tributes have been vast and
OL,7,Fincredibly touching. This is a credit
OL,8,Fto our son, and it goes to show the
OL,9,Fimpact Brodan was able to have on
OL,10,Fthose around him in his short life.
OL,11,FFor which, we can only say thank you.
OL,13,F"Wherever a beautiful soul has been,
OL,14,Fthere is a trail of beautiful
OL,15,Fmemories. With love, Dad, Mum, Corey,
OL,16,FKayla and Amelia."
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@RO]
